The,Indiana,General,Assembly,IGA,is,the,law,enacting,branch,of,the,Indiana,state,government,It,provides,the,MyIGA,Hypermedia,API,which,is,a,service,for,retrieving,information,related,to,the,IGA,This,information,covers,bills,legislators,committees,votes,actions,and,more,All,API,data,can,be,accessed,using,REST,calls,issued,in,either,JSON,or,XML,format